"&aa; provides a <literal>mod_apparmor</literal> module (package <systemitem "
"class=\"resource\">apache2-mod-apparmor</systemitem>) for the Apache program "
"(only included in &sls;). This module makes the Apache Web server ChangeHat "
"aware. Install it along with Apache."
